What you need to know:

They made the allegation five days after a bloody confrontation between police and Legion Maria adherents at Got Kwer shrine in Migori that left eight people dead.A similar fracas occurred on September 14, 2019, when goons invaded the shrine after faithful converged and injured some of them.While extending an olive branch to the faction led by Lawrence Kalul, Pope Adika urged members of Legio Maria to maintain peace despite the ongoing wrangles.